𝐑𝐚𝐢𝐥𝐰𝐚𝐲 𝐓𝐢𝐜𝐤𝐞𝐭 𝐑𝐞𝐬𝐞𝐫𝐯𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧 𝐒𝐲𝐬𝐭𝐞𝐦 (𝐉𝐚𝐯𝐚 𝐂𝐨𝐧𝐬𝐨𝐥𝐞 𝐀𝐩𝐩)

This is a simple Java-based console application that simulates a railway ticket booking system.

𝐅𝐞𝐚𝐭𝐮𝐫𝐞𝐬

⋆Book train tickets with berth preference (L/M/U/S)

⋆Cancel booked tickets using ticket ID

⋆Auto-promotion:

  RAC → Confirmed Berth

  Waiting → RAC

⋆Display:

  Confirmed tickets

  RAC queue

  Waiting list

⋆Seat preference handling and availability check

𝐌𝐨𝐝𝐮𝐥𝐞𝐬

⋆Main.java – Runs the app and handles user input

⋆Passanger.java – Stores passenger and ticket info

⋆TicketBooking.java – Manages booking, seat assignment, and display

⋆TicketCancelling.java – Handles cancellations and updates queues

𝐓𝐞𝐜𝐡𝐧𝐨𝐥𝐨𝐠𝐢𝐞𝐬 𝐔𝐬𝐞𝐝

⋆Java (OOP Concepts)

⋆Collections (ArrayList, Queue, Map)

📌 Notes

⋆RAC seats: 2

⋆Waiting list: 1

⋆Can be extended with multiple coaches
